node.text:
Walking in a @nature wonderland 😍 We can post your pictures in our account. Check the link in our bio for more info: @viewfervor (viewfervor.com)

The wonderland of Puga Valley in Ladakh, India via @apytravelstories will left you speechless 🤯 If you are a @nature lover, then you should really visit this place. It's incredible landscape attracts the visitors.

The Puga valley in the Changthang valley lies at about 22 km to the east of the Salt Lake valley across the Polokonka La pass (5,350 m). It is famous for its borax and sulphur deposits and hot water springs.

📽 @apytravelstories
📍 Puga Valley, Ladakh, India
🎶 Kathleen - Pure Imagination

node.text:
Would you dare to pass through this Via Ferrata? 😳 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on viewfervor.com (link in my bio: @viewfervor)

The new Via Ferrata Delle Aquile, on the top of Paganella, is a highly emotional and spectacular via ferrata that gives you unforgettable emotions; the sight embraces whole Trentino, but keeping fixed on the track too.

Recommendation:
Avoid the queue: purchase online your ticket and go directly to turnstile. Choose the stage and pay with your credit card. You will receive by email your ticket (you can print the ticket or save it in your smartphone), scan it on the orange scanner on the turnstile located at the gates of the lift.

📽 @niklaskoessel
📍Trentino, Italy
